org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface AknProxy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AknProxyImpl

    public interface AknProxy
    A representation of the model object 'Akn Proxy'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Pattern
    • Connection
    • Priority
    • Authorative

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getAknProxy()
